metadata.name: Everblades Chopped / Screwed
metadata.description:
CHOPPED AND SCREWED 

Everblades - the original 25 NFT's sold out on sound xyz in 2 minutes, with the music video being minted on zora and sent directly to the winner of the sound golden egg. This is the chopped and screwed version, as an airdrop to my holders. Enjoy. It's a vibe. 

Produced by Explore and KEV - Mixed by Steeziak - Cover art by Domino  
----


The original song can be heard on all streaming platforms including spotify / audius, or in your wallet via the NFT on opensea - or the music video on youtube.

https://opensea.io/collection/dominosmusic
